    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a reliable option for someone looking for a solid driver that may need a little TLC. While the engine and transmission are functional, you should expect some cosmetic imperfections, including minor scratches on the exterior and visible wear on the interior upholstery. It has been a dependable vehicle, but it is approaching a point where some routine maintenance, like a brake service or new tires, will be needed soon. Overall, it's a honest car that performs its duties well but shows its age and mileage.",
